&lt;p&gt;The recipient of &lt;strong&gt;#30 Asia&amp;#8217;s 50 Best Restaurants 2014&lt;/strong&gt;, Best Dining Experience at the 2014 CNBC Awaaz Travel Awards and Conde Nast Traveler&rsquo;s 2013 Gold Standard Award for Best Traditional Restaurant, Dum Pukht is a restaurant not to be missed in New Delhi. Dum Pukht is a cooking style where foods are slow roasted in a sealed pot, cooking in spices, herbs and their own juices. The ambiance is of refined old world elegance and service is polished and charming. Attire is smart casual.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Contact Dum Pukhtby phone at +(91) (11) 2611 2233 or email &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:mytable.itcmaurya@itchotels.in&quot;&gt;mytable.itcmaurya@itchotels.in&lt;/a&gt; to book your reservation&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection to receive your special benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to dine, number of guests, preferred time, cell or local (hotel) phone number&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reconfirmation Policy: Please provide a cell phone number or local (hotel) contact number in New Delhi. Dum Pukhtwill call you on the dining date to reconfirm&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
